On a volcano!

28
00:01:02,479 --> 00:01:04,360
The meeting faces many challenges,

29
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:06,180
like dangerous roads!

30
00:01:06,180 --> 00:01:07,680
Lava explosions!

31
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:10,800
And electric rocks shaped like letters!

32
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:11,890
But when the road starts to

33
