crumble underneath them,

34
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:15,530
these five rivals will join together

35
00:01:15,530 --> 00:01:18,010
and accomplish the impossible!

36
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:20,250
Jumping over a cliff!

37
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:22,361
Wow, the BRICS Summit

38
00:01:22,361 --> 00:01:23,520
must be so cool!

39
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:26,080
Let’s take a look at the actual footage.

40
